'''巴西頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Brazilton'''}}）為位在[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[克勞福德縣_(堪薩斯州)|克勞福德縣]]的[[非建制地區|非建制地區]]，坐落在[[3號堪薩斯州州道|3號堪薩斯州州道]]上<ref>{{cite map|publisher=Kansas Department of Transportation|title=Official State Transportation Map|edition=2007-2008|section=F12}}</ref>。

==歷史==
此社區之名稱於1882年由居住於此的農民托馬斯·巴西（Thomas Brazil）所命名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=RRM1AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA307#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=A Twentieth Century History and Biographical Record of Crawford County, Kansas | publisher=The Lewis Publishing Company | year=1905 | pages=307 | access-date=2016-04-12 | archive-date=2014-07-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725115746/http://books.google.com/books?id=RRM1AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA307#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4483 | title=Profile for Brazilton, Kansas | publisher=ePodunk | accessdate=8 June 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064003/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4483 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

此社區境內的郵政局於1882年10月5日開設，期間持續營運直到1966年6月17日終止<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CR |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=6 June 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009124740/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CR |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

此社區在[[艾奇遜，托皮卡和聖塔菲鐵路|艾奇遜，托皮卡和聖塔菲鐵路]]匹茲堡和查紐特（Pittsburg & Chanute）支線上設有車站及裝運點<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA232#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Embracing Events, Institutions, Industries, Counties, Cities, Towns, Prominent Persons, Etc. | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=232}}</ref>。

